author: hiranya
msg: Implementing support for multiple SSL configurations at HTTPS transport sender. See SYNAPSE-563 for details. This patch introduces an optional transport sender parameter named "customSSLProfiles". A new IOEventDispatch is provided which supports manipulating multiple SSLContext instances. Still a single IOReactor and a threadpool is used by the sender.
